WEBVTT

00:06.798 --> 00:08.084
<i>If you're watching this...</i>

00:09.968 --> 00:11.504
<i>it means I probably didn't make it.</i>

00:13.347 --> 00:15.213
<i>Sarah, Wendell, Charlie.</i>

00:16.767 --> 00:18.554
<i>It's on to you to do what I couldn't.</i>

00:20.771 --> 00:21.887
<i>Just know that I tried.</i>

00:23.000 --> 00:29.074
